[Although the case number has slowly increased towards 200, the
investigation has come up with multiple "smoking guns" (bags of spinach
with the outbreak strain isolated) and localized the source essentially to
a single place on a single day on a single shift. How the spinach became
contaminated is still unclear. - Mod.LL]
